summary: AN ORDINANCE accepting a formal land transfer agreement between the City of Seattle and the State of Washington consistent with the direction provided by Council Resolutions 27196, 27901, and 28035, authorizing the execution of such contracts and documents as are required to implement the aforementioned agreement, authorizing the necessary appropriation to make the necessary transfers, authorizing the sale of the improved properties identified in the agreement, and designating the disposition of sales proceeds.
